  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示feature分支如何合并到main分支的过程。另外，我想把feature设为主分支，这样视觉上更突出开发主线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature",
        "main",
        "merge",
        "mainBranchName"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，就是把feature作为默认展示的主分支，main反而作为次要分支。那分支的显示顺序上，feature排在main前面吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature",
        "main",
        "mainBranchOrder",
        "order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，feature的order设为1，main设为0，这样feature在右边，main在左边。还有，需要显示分支名称和提交标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature",
        "main",
        "showBranches",
        "showCommitLabel",
        "order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我配置好了显示选项。现在feature分支先有一个提交f，然后从feature切出main分支，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature",
        "commit f",
        "branch main",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "顺序有点问题——应该是先在feature上提交f，然后切到feature再做提交g，接着再切到main做提交b。不是从feature切main之后马上切回去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature",
        "commit g",
        "checkout feature",
        "checkout main"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了，我调整一下：feature提交f，保持feature当前状态再提交g，然后切到main提交b。接下来是把feature合并到main吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge feature",
        "main",
        "commit b"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，main在提交b之后合并feature，合并完main再提交d结束整个流程。另外调试信息要打开，方便检查配置是否正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge feature",
        "commit d",
        "logLevel",
        "debug"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。feature作为主分支在右侧，依次有f和g两个提交；main在左侧，先有b，然后合并feature，最后提交d。调试模式也启用了，你可以验收一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature",
        "main",
        "commit f",
        "commit g",
        "commit b",
        "commit d",
        "merge feature",
        "logLevel debug"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
